million, just ahead of ``Say Anything,'' which also earned $2.3
million.
   Oscar-winning ``Rain Man'' remained in the top 10 at seventh
place with $1.7 million. ``Loverboy,'' starring Patrick Dempsey as
a college kid who delivers pizza and more made a weak debut in
eighth place with $1.6 million.
   ``Field of Dreams'' earned $1.5 million for ninth place, and
``She's Out of Control'' was No. 10 with $1.3 million.
   Here are the top movies for the weekend as tallied by Exhibitor
Relations Co., with distributor, weekend gross, number of theater
