fair; Los Angeles 58 foggy; Phoenix 74 fair; Salt Lake City 50
fair; San Diego 59 cloudy; San Francisco 55 fair; Seattle 51 partly
cloudy.
   _Canada: Montreal 54 rain; Toronto 39 rain.
