<TEXT>
   The president of NBC News says a big part
of his job is answering really tough questions _ like why Willard
Scott wears a toupee on the ``Today'' show.
   ``I don't know why Willard Scott wears a toupee in New York but
not on the road,'' Michael G. Gartner said Monday in a speech at
